    <section name="About Harvest Tool">
      <p>The Harvest Tool provides functionality for capturing and registering product metadata. The tool will run locally at the Discipline Node to crawl the local data repository in order to discover products and register associated metadata with the Registry Service.
      </p>

      <p>Please send comments, change requests and bug reports to the <a href="mailto:pds_operator@jpl.nasa.gov">PDS Operator</a> at pds_operator@jpl.nasa.gov.
      </p>
